  "tasbihatArba3Info": "Dalam fikih Syiah, Tasbiḥāt al-Arbaʿa geugantoe Surah al-Fatiha bak rakaʿat keu-3 ngon keu-4 Dhuhr, Asr, Maghrib, ngon Isha. Wajib (wājib) geubaca sigohlom, dan disunahkan (mustaḥabb) geubaca teulông kali.",
