  "tasbihatZahraOriginLabel": "Asal",
  "tasbihatZahraHadith": "Sayyidah Fatima al-Zahra (sa) meuhaba bak Nabi ﷺ minta saboh pelayan. Geukheun: \"Peue hana Lon pitudôh droeneuh saboh nyang leubèh get nibak nyan? Baca Subḥānallāh 33 kali, Alḥamdulillāh 33 kali, ngon Allāhu Akbar 34 kali lheueh tiap salat. Nyan leubèh get keu droeneuh nibak saboh pelayan.\"",
